divs: Sighting DetailsI started to be woke up at 3:33am about 2008.first sighting lights Flashed Sequentially.white lights.2nd sighting pale orange lights looked liked stars blinked on then off one at a time,about ten lights.they have communicated with me, they know my thoughts.numbers i see in my mind.333,11 22 888.have seen Black Helicopter up close, not a helicopter something very advanced.Have seen Triangles but i think their Military.I think they are Advanced Humans.the one that communicated with me is a female.she said she is God.
Summary: Lights Flashed Sequentially....lights were white...3:33am wake up call
